sub_title: Chief Executive Officer at Open Closet Lgbt Netherlands
summary:
In twenty-three (23) years of experience working in the Hospitality industry. I have developed several qualities, which make me an asset in the workplace. Notable among these are: -
●	Team spirit and ability to work with others to achieve objectives.
●	Work under pressure, independently and to a high standard.
●	Attention to details, satisfaction, quality and effective services.
●	Ability to relate to people at all levels within professionalism and courteousness.
●	Welcome challenges and opportunities for growth. Good Organizational, Interpersonal skills, Fast Learner, Dependable and Conflict resolution.
●	Exceptional customer services, Communication skill	
•	Sales, Cash management and processing financial transactions, Inventory management system
